'''NullComm''' was a large communications corporation during the height of the [[Galactic Empire/Legends|Galactic Empire]]. NullComm was well known for less than admirable business practices. Their business became successful through ruthlessly exploiting lesser companies.<ref name="CCW">''[[Coruscant and the Core Worlds]]''</ref>

